---
title: Venison Steak & Caramelised Onion Sub with Pear Salad, Mustard Mayo & Cheddar
description: Here’s a delicious, decadent and devilishly fast venison steak sub. Kiwi-spiced venison is cooked just to your liking and sat atop a perfectly toasted panini slathered in mustard and mayo. Add saucy sweetness with caramelised onion - it’s sure to be love at first bite.
